title: Ep 95 - Change Your Beliefs, Change Your Life
itunes:title: Ep 95 - Change Your Beliefs, Change Your Life
description:
What you believe about yourself will directly affect what you will become. Here is the truth - most of us are held back by our beliefs about ourselves and only that. In this episode I talk about the importance of your beliefs and the easiest way to change them to make the life you want.
